   calculated for both combining states, as well as Franck-Condon factor
   and r-centroids for the first negative system in the (CO)-C-12-O-16 (+)
   molecule. Furthermore, we report the value of the electronic isotopic
   shift Deltav(e) = -0.395 cm(-1) of the B --> X system in (CO)-C-13-O-16
   (+) , calculated on the basis the presents results and those obtained by
   us previously for the (CO)-C-13-O-16 (+) molecule.},
